item.title: CVE-2022-32189|2024-08-03T07:32:56.026Z -- go%20standard%20library -- math%2Fbig
item.description: A too-short encoded message can cause a panic in Float.GobDecode and Rat GobDecode in math/big in Go before 1.17.13 and 1.18.5, potentially allowing a denial of service.
